comments: Dort (OKC) slightly moves toward White (BOS) and marginal body contact occurs as they come together at the end of the drive.
Dort (OKC) lowers his arm and makes contact with Porzingis (BOS) as he contests the shot near the rim.
Tatum (BOS) brings his forearm to Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) side and marginal body contact occurs during the drive.
Dort (OKC) grabs and pulls Brown's (BOS) jersey away from his body, which dislodges him from his rebounding position.
Holmgren (OKC) establishes himself in Pritchard's (BOS) path and he absorbs the side to side contact during the pick.
Williams (OKC) is releasing away from the contact with Pritchard (BOS), and incidental foot to foot contact occurs as they come together at the same spot.
Brown (BOS) extends his right arm forward and initiates illegal contact with Williams' (OKC) arm, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Williams (OKC) does not maintain verticality, and makes contact with Tatum's (BOS) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Porzingis (BOS) is already in Dort's (OKC) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Tatum (BOS) is moving alongside Williams' (OKC) path and marginal contact occurs as they come together at the same spot.
Tatum (BOS) brings his arms slightly forward as he establishes screening position in Holmgren's (OKC) path, and the contact during the screen is marginal.
Dort (OKC) moves forward slightly towards Tatum (BOS) and marginal contact occurs as Tatum is passing the ball.
Holmgren (OKC) brings his arm down and makes contact with Porzingis' (BOS) head as he defends the shot attempt.
Pritchard (BOS) and Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) mutually engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs off-ball.
Tatum (BOS) brings his hand towards Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) upper body, and the contact as Gilgeous-Alexander passes the ball is marginal.
White (BOS) steps into Giddey's (OKC) space and delivers body contact that affects his SQBR at the start of the drive.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court (successful 2 pt. basket) stood as called.
Brown (BOS) immediately slides his hand off of Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) side and marginal contact occurs as the two come together off-ball.
Brown (BOS) commits a take foul on Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC).
Williams (OKC) legally contests Brown's (BOS) jump shot attempt.
